title: 859 W. Fletcher St Unit CH
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 238623512', 'Rent: $4,795 / Month', 'Beds: 5', 'Bath: 3', 'Available Date: 07/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats Only', 'Parking:: street parking', 'This wonderful Victorian building is tucked away on a quiet tree lined street, yet is in the very heart of Lakeview, steps from Halsted and Clark Streets.', 'Belmont Avenue, which is just a block north, has a number of local boutiques and charming restaurants as well as the CTA El stop with connections to the Red, Brown, and Purple Express Lines.', 'Surrounding major streets also have a variety of dining and entertainment options including several theaters.', 'Lake Shore Drive and Chicago’s lakefront are located two blocks east.', 'This provides easy commuter transportation as well as a number of outdoor activities including biking, running, golf, and lounging on the beach.', 'The #22 Clark street bus stop is less than a block away and offers a quick route to downtown all night long.', 'We offer a hassle-free full online leasing process featuring online applications, lease signing, and payment options.', 'NO SECURITY DEPOSIT!', '$150.00 Application Fee Per Person', '$100.00 Move-in Fee Per Bedroom', 'NO DOGS, Cats ok!', 'Advertised rent prices are subject to change without notice!', 'Chicago Apartment Place Inc.', '773.472.3713']
